data.description:
INSTANT EQUITY..... SOLD AS IS | SELLER WILL PAY BUYER CLOSING ALLOWANCE WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER!!!

Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Magnolia Springs neighborhood! Location is prime and this young home decided you were the ONE for it!!!  Located north of I-10 and in the county with no flood insurance required this home allows for instant equity with a little TLC. 

This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem, featuring the popular Cali floorplan, is a true showstopper. With an attractive brick and vinyl exterior, this home boasts both style and functionality in a package just under 1800 sqft. This home also has the builders warranty still affixed to transfer to the next buyer.

As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the luxury vinyl flooring that not only adds a touch of elegance but also ensures durability and easy maintenance. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's delight, showcasing beautiful granite countertops with under-mount sinks throughout. The stainless steel appliance package is the perfect complement, making meal preparation a breeze.

Lighting is key, and this home doesn't disappoint. Recessed lights throughout the living spaces create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The master suite is a true retreat with double vanities in the master bath, a relaxing soaking tub, and a separate shower. Getting ready in the morning will be a pleasure.

The outdoor space is just as impressive as the interior, with a fully sodded lawn and meticulous landscaping that adds to the curb appeal. You'll enjoy the benefits of energy-efficient features such as vinyl Low-E tilt-in windows, a high-efficiency 14-Seer HVAC system, and a central heat pump heating system.

Did we mention the alarm and monitoring system remains!!

Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Call us today to schedule your showing and make this exceptional property in the perfect location your forever home.
